      • isFkOptimizationAllowed

        @Deprecated(forRemoval=true,

public static boolean isFkOptimizationAllowed​(SqmPath<?> sqmPath)
        Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
        Use isFkOptimizationAllowed(SqmPath, EntityAssociationMapping) instead
        Utility that returns false when the provided sqmPath is a join that cannot be dereferenced through the foreign key on the associated table, i.e. a join that's neither SqmJoinType.INNER nor SqmJoinType.LEFT or one that has an explicit on clause predicate.

        Utility that returns false when the provided sqmPath is a join that cannot be dereferenced through the foreign key on the associated table, i.e. a join that's neither SqmJoinType.INNER nor SqmJoinType.LEFT or one that has an explicit on clause predicate.
